snippet.title: #19 Outer Space Combat - Interton VC4000
snippet.description:
This is a fun game for the Interton, but a bit limited in gameplay. Basically two gamemodes in one or two player and fast or slow speed.
Blogpost: http://retro-spill.blogspot.com/2014/04/outer-space-combat-19-vc-4000.html
